OL,6,FPolice and Crime Commissioner Philip
OL,7,FWilkinson said, "I'm reassured that
OL,8,Fdespite more than 50 weapon sweeps by
OL,9,Fneighbourhood officers no weapons were
OL,10,Ffound, but I am concerned that one in
OL,11,Fthree shops failed the test purchases
OL,12,Fand sold knives to underage police
OL,13,Fcadets."
OL,15,FAs part of the week long Operation
OL,16,FSceptre, 30 knives and bladed articles
OL,17,Fwere surrendered in the six surrender
OL,18,Fbins. Thirty-two stop searches were
OL,19,Fconducted, with one knife found and
OL,20,Ftwo knife related arrests were made.
